data.description: This 3BR 2BA is located in the Lake Jordan subdivision and needs a new owner. It is within walking distance to Matilda Harris Elementary and Camden Middle School. This home includes a split floor plan with a huge family room and a large open kitchen. The kitchen has lots of counter space, along with plenty of cabinets. The master bedroom has a nice walk-in closet, and the master bath includes a larger soaker tub. This home has a fenced back yard and a 2-car garage. Schedule a showing today. Seller to contribute up to $12,000 to be used as buyer closing cost and or to buy down interest rate.
